              },
              "free_text": [
                " TO OBTAIN THE HE PRO-",
                " DUCTION CROSS SECTION, THE (N,A)-ACTIVATION",
                " CROSS SECTION WAS USED AS A STANDARD. THE RESIDUAL",
                " ACTIVITY OF THE SAMPLES WERE MEASURED WITH AN",
                " ABSOLUTELY CALIBRATED GELI DETECTOR."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".DISKS OF 10 MM DIAMETER BY 0.5 MM THICK ALUMINIUM",
                " WITH A CHEMICAL PURITY OF 99.99 PERCENT. THE SAMPLES",
                " WERE ASSEMBLED AS A SANDWICH AND WRAPPED WITH THIN",
                " AL FOIL TO EXCLUDE ALPHA-PARTICLE LOSS FROM THEM."
              ]
            }
